Y = list(deg_Real.values())
sns.barplot(x = Y, y = X, palette = "magma")
plt.xticks(range(0, max(Y)+5, 2))
plt.ylabel("Player Jersey number")
plt.xlabel("degree")
plt.title("Player pass degrees for Real Madrid vs Liverpool", size = 16)
plt.show()
```

